{"id": "gna1665702540285", "title": "webgen", "breadcrumbs": ["Uniface Reference", "ProcScript Reference", "ProcScript: Statements", "webgen"], "url": "https://docs.rocketsoftware.com/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html", "html": "<html><body><header class=\"zDocsTopicPageHead\"><h1 class=\"css-g931ng\">webgen</h1><div class=\"zDocsTopicActions\" role=\"list\"><div class=\"zDocsBundlePagination\" data-testid=\"next-prev-container\" role=\"listitem\"><div class=\"zDocsPrevTopicButton zDocsPrevTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Previous: webdefinitions \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Previous: webdefinitions \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mez1665702540201.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-prev\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-prev\"></use></svg></a></span></div><div class=\"zDocsNextTopicButton zDocsNextTopicButton\"><span class=\"\"><a aria-label=\"Next: webget   \" class=\"\" data-tooltip-content=\"Next: webget   \" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" data-tooltip-open=\"false\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hbu1719365402351.html\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></a></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsMyDocsMenu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Add to My Topics\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Add to My Topics\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" id=\"addToMyDocsDropdownTrigger\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-bookmark-add\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-bookmark-add\"></use></svg>Add to My Topics</span><div aria-labelledby=\"pdfDropdown\" class=\"dropdown-menu dropdown-menu-right\"><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub\">Add selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html?finish_action=mydocs_topic_and_sub_head\">Add Topic &amp; Subtopics with topic head</a><a class=\"zDocsAddTopicButton zDocsMyDocsMenuItem dropdown-item\" href=\"/de-DE/auth/login?redirect=/bundle/uniface_104/page/gna1665702540285.html?finish_action=mydocs_pub\">Add entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsWatchButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Watch\" class=\"d-lg-flex d-none zDocsSubscribeButton\" data-tooltip-content=\"Watch\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsSubscribeButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-eye zDocsSubscribeButton\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-eye\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsSubscribeButton\">Watch</span></span></div><div class=\"zDocsExportPdfMenu zDocsExportMenu\" data-testid=\"export-pdf-menu\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Download PDF\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Download PDF\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#ZdExportPDFModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-pdf\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-pdf\"></use></svg>Download PDF</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527927\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2527927\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 08, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gna1665702540285.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gna1665702540285.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gna1665702540285.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gna1665702540285\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"gna1665702540285__webgen_247653\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of\n      a static server page.</p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d79241e1_d79242e1_d79243e1\">\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104gna1665702540285_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"gna1665702540285__codeblock_i15_kbz_bwb\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">webgen{/append}  {LayoutFile}  {,OutputFile}</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__section_w2545ab1b7b5_w2546ab1b7_w2547ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__p_d79247e1_d79248e1_d79249e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">webgen</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d52112e1_d52113e1_d52114e1_d52115e1_d52116e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d96205e74\">Qualifiers</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7766e1_d7767e1_d7768e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Qualifiers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7766e1_d7767e1_d7768e1__entry__1\">Qualifier</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7766e1_d7767e1_d7768e1__entry__2\">Description</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7766e1_d7767e1_d7768e1__entry__1\"><span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/append</span>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7766e1_d7767e1_d7768e1__entry__2\">Appends the generated XHTML document to an\n                        existing <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>. If <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>\n                        does not exist, a new file is created. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d52117e1_d52118e1_d52119e1_d52120e1_d52121e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d96205e125\">Parameters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__1\">Parameter </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__2\">Data Type </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LayoutFile</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__3\">Name of the file to be used as a layout\n                        definition of the server page; maximum length of 79 bytes. No default\n                        extension is provided for <var class=\"keyword varname\">LayoutFile</var>.<p class=\"p\">If\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">LayoutFile</var> does not exist, the layout definition of\n                           a server page is determined by the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$SEARCH_SKELETON</span>\n                           assignment setting.</p></td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__2\">String </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7769e1_d7770e1_d7771e1__entry__3\">Name of the file to contain the generated\n                        document; string, with a maximum length of 79 bytes. No default extension is\n                        provided for <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>.<p class=\"p\">If\n                              <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var> does not exist, a new file is created.\n                           If <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var> exists, that file is overwritten, unless\n                           the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">/append</span> switch is used.</p></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d52122e1_d52123e1_d52124e1_d52125e1_d52126e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d96205e219\">Return Values</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span></span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__1\">Value</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__2\">Explanation</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__2\">No errors detected, all field values\n                        transferred. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__1\"> &lt; <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__2\">An error occurred.\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains the exact error.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__1\"> &gt; <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7772e1_d7773e1_d7774e1__entry__2\">Number of times that an unknown field or entity\n                        in the layout definition was skipped while preparing the XHTML document.\n                           <p class=\"p\">If the layout definition contains references to fields or entities\n                           that are not present in the component definition, this is not considered\n                           an error. The affected part of the layout is simply skipped. However, the\n                           total number of fields and entities skipped is reported in\n                              <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span>.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gna1665702540285__note_w2548ab1b7c11b5_w2549ab1b7c11_w2550ab1b7_w2551ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is recommended that you always\n      check the value of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> after <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webget</span> and before\n        <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>.</div>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 4. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> commonly returned by\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">Value </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">Error constant</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">Meaning</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-31</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UGENERR_LICENSE&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">No license for requested action. Contact your\n                        Uniface representative.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-250</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UWEBERR_SKELETON&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">Layout definition not found or incorrect. For\n                        example, the layout is in a separate skeleton file that is not\n                        available.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-251</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UWEBERR_OUTFILE&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">When <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$web</span> is empty, the\n                        output file is not specified or is the same as the layout file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-252</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UWEBERR_IO&gt;</code>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">Could not write output file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-253</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UWEBERR_IO_IMAGE&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">Could not write image file.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">-254</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__2\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">&lt;UWEBERR_ITERATION&gt;</code></td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gna1665702540285__table_d7775e1_d7776e1_d7777e1__entry__3\">Nested iteration over the same entity.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d52127e1_d52128e1_d52129e1_d52130e1_d52131e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d96205e449\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__d5934e20\">Use in Static Server Page components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gna1665702540285__topic_d52132e1_d52133e1_d52134e1_d52135e1_d52136e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d96205e458\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__p_d79268e1_d79269e1_d79270e1\">The <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> statement generates an\n            XHTML document from the layout definitions of a static server page, replacing any field\n            values (marked by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;x-subst&gt;</span> and\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;x-occurrence&gt;</span> elements) with the current values in the\n            component definition. The layout definition may be part of the USP or it may be stored\n            in an external <var class=\"keyword varname\">LayoutFile</var>.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gna1665702540285__li_d33500e1_d33501e1_d33502e1\">If no parameters are specified,\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> defaults to the current component name for the layout\n               definition and output file.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gna1665702540285__li_d33503e1_d33504e1_d33505e1\">If the application was started by the Web Request\n               Dispatcher (<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$web=\"wrd\"</span>) and the <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>\n               argument is omitted, the generated document is passed to the web server.</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gna1665702540285__li_d33506e1_d33507e1_d33508e1\">If the <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var> argument is\n               specified, the generated document is written to the\n               <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var>.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__p_d79271e1_d79272e1_d79273e1\">The names of <var class=\"keyword varname\">LayoutFile</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">OutputFile</var> are subject to non-DBMS file assignments in the [FILES] section of the assignment file.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__p_d79274e1_d79275e1_d79276e1\">Always do a <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">store</span> operation before\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>, because <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span> creates different XHTML\n            for fields that are stored in a database.</p>\n<div class=\"note note note_note\" id=\"gna1665702540285__note_w2552ab1b7c15c11_w2553ab1b7c15_w2554ab1b7_w2555ab1\"><span class=\"note__title\">Note:</span> It is\n            possible to customize the XHTML generated by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">webgen</span>. You can generate\n            unique <code class=\"ph codeph\">id</code> attributes for fields, generate label elements with\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">for</code> attributes, and add customized code such as JavaScript to the\n            generated output.</div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gna1665702540285__p_d79277e1_d79278e1_d79279e1\">When an entity in the USP layout is surrounded by <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;x-occurrence&gt;</span> tags, HTML fields are created for each occurrence currently in the component definition. To mark which occurrence is shown, the occurrence number is added to each field name. Outside <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">&lt;x-occurrence&gt;</span> tags, no occurrence number is added because it is assumed to be <code class=\"ph codeph\">1</code>.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hbu1719365402351.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>webget</a><p>Load data from a client request into a static server page (USP), reconnect to the database if applicable, set a current occurrence, and activate a detail or error trigger, if required.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zbc1665702583540.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>web</a><p>Declares that the trigger or operation can be called from a web client, or that its data can be included in the DSP request-response exchange of other triggers or operations.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/urh1665702755394.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in</a><p>Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527927\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2527927\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "webgen Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 08, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Generate an XHTML document from the layout definition and the component definition of a static server page. Explain this code webgen{/append} {LayoutFile} {,OutputFile} Copy Example: webgen Qualifiers Table 1. Qualifiers Qualifier Description /append Appends the generated XHTML document to an existing OutputFile . If OutputFile does not exist, a new file is created. Parameters Table 2. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description LayoutFile String Name of the file to be used as a layout definition of the server page; maximum length of 79 bytes. No default extension is provided for LayoutFile . If LayoutFile does not exist, the layout definition of a server page is determined by the $SEARCH_SKELETON assignment setting. OutputFile String Name of the file to contain the generated document; string, with a maximum length of 79 bytes. No default extension is provided for OutputFile . If OutputFile does not exist, a new file is created. If OutputFile exists, that file is overwritten, unless the /append switch is used. Return Values Table 3. Values returned in $status Value Explanation 0 No errors detected, all field values transferred. < 0 An error occurred. $procerror contains the exact error. > 0 Number of times that an unknown field or entity in the layout definition was skipped while preparing the XHTML document. If the layout definition contains references to fields or entities that are not present in the component definition, this is not considered an error. The affected part of the layout is simply skipped. However, the total number of fields and entities skipped is reported in $status . Note: It is recommended that you always check the value of $procerror after webget and before webgen . Table 4. Values of $procerror commonly returned by webgen Value Error constant Meaning -31 <UGENERR_LICENSE> No license for requested action. Contact your Uniface representative. -250 <UWEBERR_SKELETON> Layout definition not found or incorrect. For example, the layout is in a separate skeleton file that is not available. -251 <UWEBERR_OUTFILE> When $web is empty, the output file is not specified or is the same as the layout file. -252 <UWEBERR_IO> Could not write output file. -253 <UWEBERR_IO_IMAGE> Could not write image file. -254 <UWEBERR_ITERATION> Nested iteration over the same entity. Use Use in Static Server Page components. Description The webgen statement generates an XHTML document from the layout definitions of a static server page, replacing any field values (marked by <x-subst> and <x-occurrence> elements) with the current values in the component definition. The layout definition may be part of the USP or it may be stored in an external LayoutFile . If no parameters are specified, webgen defaults to the current component name for the layout definition and output file. If the application was started by the Web Request Dispatcher ( $web=\"wrd\" ) and the OutputFile argument is omitted, the generated document is passed to the web server. If the OutputFile argument is specified, the generated document is written to the OutputFile . The names of LayoutFile and OutputFile are subject to non-DBMS file assignments in the [FILES] section of the assignment file. Always do a store operation before webgen , because webgen creates different XHTML for fields that are stored in a database. Note: It is possible to customize the XHTML generated by webgen . You can generate unique id attributes for fields, generate label elements with for attributes, and add customized code such as JavaScript to the generated output. When an entity in the USP layout is surrounded by <x-occurrence> tags, HTML fields are created for each occurrence currently in the component definition. To mark which occurrence is shown, the occurrence number is added to each field name. Outside <x-occurrence> tags, no occurrence number is added because it is assumed to be 1 . Related Links webget Load data from a client request into a static server page (USP), reconnect to the database if applicable, set a current occurrence, and activate a detail or error trigger, if required. web Declares that the trigger or operation can be called from a web client, or that its data can be included in the DSP request-response exchange of other triggers or operations. Creating a Web Output Filter Plug-in Uniface provides a generic mechanism that enables you to add your own JavaScript or HTML to web pages generated from dynamic and static server pages. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}